{"tid":1689612,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果想做冷氣軍師，連登仔麻煩讀下書","createTime":"2019-11-03T02:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T10:30:52.000Z","uid":50457,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e679bfd62529735548a49ef12cde5bbe2940a120","tid":1689612,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=xtJNCwAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PA64&amp;lpg=PA64&amp;dq=%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=m7lMLvUOgP&amp;sig=ACfU3U0RxouTyGcnhSpN3zOkk96B1OErPg&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwje9Kih98zlAhXKLqYKHRfuA8AQ6AEwAnoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DxtJNCwAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPA64%26lpg%3DPA64%26dq%3D%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%25AD%2596%25E7%2595%25A5%26source%3Dbl%26ots%3Dm7lMLvUOgP%26sig%3DACfU3U0RxouTyGcnhSpN3zOkk96B1OErPg%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D2ahUKEwje9Kih98zlAhXKLqYKHRfuA8AQ6AEwAnoECAkQAQ%23v%3Donepage%26q%26f%3Dfalse&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpNLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=a534f404\" target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=xtJNCwAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PA64&amp;lpg=PA64&amp;dq=%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=m7lMLvUOgP&amp;sig=ACfU3U0RxouTyGcnhSpN3zOkk96B1OErPg&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwje9Kih98zlAhXKLqYKHRfuA8AQ6AEwAnoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false</a><br />\n<br />\n好詳細解釋人群控制係啲乜，點解要人群控制，同埋唔同的策略。<br />\n<br />\n雖然係台灣情況，但好多都值得睇，同有用...<br />\n<br />\n案例寫到去佔中<br />\n<br />\n例如人數一多，人的獨立思考就會消失，結果身邊的人走，自己跟住走。雖然無話點樣拆解，但已經詳細描述現在大部份黑警人群管制方法。<br />\n<br />\n260頁，比真冷氣軍睇，除左GEAR，知識都要UP GRADE<br />\n<br />\n希望有更多真冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f64efc913fd1ad54f95ea5e15619996602b42e0","tid":1689612,"uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"點解成日被人當綿羊咁舞嚟舞去，入面有解釋群眾心理學<br />\n<br />\n一手硬，一手軟又點解需要咁做,勇武有時間都要讀下書"},{"pid":"8f11262293b2333f4895efb617e7bb218eb3a008","tid":1689612,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:13:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8812ace8947d5928baea3eaa5a11f38e4cb223e4","tid":1689612,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:16:58.000Z","msg":"點解一次又一次都損兵折將，係因為大家都未讀好書"},{"pid":"ed6e42d24bc3590679a65cb3577b0f2e197cc64c","tid":1689612,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:28:35.000Z","msg":"想街頭抗爭，更需要知道策略"},{"pid":"743f4d5fdea6f8bcdb42ecc10ce0965fca9d6aa4","tid":1689612,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:43:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9af13514a360d257a3eeed620b104e25121e61a5","tid":1689612,"uid":182637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"此post值推"},{"pid":"2be18cfac77afb94fb5f6f8a74b9c782f1eeeeb9","tid":1689612,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e679bfd62529735548a49ef12cde5bbe2940a120","tid":1689612,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T02:06:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=xtJNCwAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PA64&amp;lpg=PA64&amp;dq=%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=m7lMLvUOgP&amp;sig=ACfU3U0RxouTyGcnhSpN3zOkk96B1OErPg&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwje9Kih98zlAhXKLqYKHRfuA8AQ6AEwAnoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DxtJNCwAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPA64%26lpg%3DPA64%26dq%3D%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E7%25AD%2596%25E7%2595%25A5%26source%3Dbl%26ots%3Dm7lMLvUOgP%26sig%3DACfU3U0RxouTyGcnhSpN3zOkk96B1OErPg%26hl%